data.description: Darling single story home located in an established neighborhood just minutes from Hwy 151 & Loop 410 and less than 15 minutes to Lackland AFB.  The interior features a flexible floor plan with 3 bedrooms, 2 full bathrooms and a bonus space between the secondary bedrooms and the primary suite that could be used as a home office, second living space or 4th bedroom.  The main living spaces feature laminate and ceramic tile flooring for easy maintenance, recessed lighting and a handsome chair rail accent.  The eat in kitchen overlooks the main living area and opens to the covered patio overlooking the privacy fenced backyard with no immediate neighbors in back. Recent improvements include new carpet, fresh interior paint, repaired back fence and refreshed landscaping in front.  Additional features include a two car garage with opener, laundry room with full size washer/dryer connections, programmable thermostat and more.  Same day showings available.
